org.elasticsearch.index.codec.docvaluesformat

Interface DocValuesFormatProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDocValuesFormatProvider, DefaultDocValuesFormatProvider, PreBuiltDocValuesFormatProvider

    public interface DocValuesFormatProvider
    A DocValuesFormatProvider acts as a named container for specific DocValuesFormat implementations. Custom DocValuesFormat implementations can be exposed via CodecModule.addDocValuesFormat(String, Class)
    See Also:
    CodecModule
